\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa359c93bd1a12901d669a1af25d206463fdcaa","tid":2411182,"uid":301529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"十五年咁重？林以晴深藍嚟？<br />\n以香港法治依啲case應該3-4年貨仔"},{"pid":"d8640d4eef40980cb7db583a31e39c9131f17932","tid":2411182,"uid":247211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"可惜唔係當差<br />\n係既告返條女襲警都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0faf7e45d13fc31cb7308daeb92bafe1f811381","tid":2411182,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db17553412ae26e5830d599e47b7d1b33f56bbc6","tid":2411182,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"技安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd30b556b7ec3ddb53511939fcfd5c92afb9002c","tid":2411182,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:30:31.000Z","msg":"高尚情操斬到人危殆都係判45個月<br />\n實要上訴搏下啦"}]}